                "markupText" : "<html lang=\"en\" class=\"govuk-template \">    <head>      \t<meta charset=\"utf-8\">      \t<title> Cookies </title>      \t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover\">      \t<meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#0b0c0c\">            \t<meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">              \t<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" sizes=\"16x16 32x32 48x48\" href=\"/govuk/assets/images/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\">        \t<link rel=\"mask-icon\" href=\"/govuk/assets/images/govuk-mask-icon.svg\" color=\"#0b0c0c\">         \t<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"/govuk/assets/images/govuk-apple-touch-icon-180x180.png\">        \t<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"167x167\" href=\"/govuk/assets/images/govuk-apple-touch-icon-167x167.png\">        \t<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"152x152\" href=\"/govuk/assets/images/govuk-apple-touch-icon-152x152.png\">        \t<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/govuk/assets/images/govuk-apple-touch-icon.png\">              <!--[if lte IE 8]><link href=\"/public/stylesheets/application-ie8.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><![endif]--> <!--[if gt IE 8]><!--><link href=\"/public/stylesheets/application.css\" media=\"all\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><!--<![endif]-->       </head>    \t\t<body class=\"govuk-template__body \">      \t\t<script>document.body.className = ((document.body.className) ? document.body.className + ' js-enabled' : 'js-enabled');</script>                  <a href=\"#main-content\" class=\"govuk-skip-link\" data-module=\"govuk-skip-link\">Skip to main content</a> <main class=\"govuk-main-wrapper govuk-main-wrapper--auto-spacing\" id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\">            <div class=\"govuk-grid-row\">     <div class=\"govuk-grid-column-two-thirds govuk-body-m govuk-body\">        \t\t\t<h1 class=\"govuk-heading-l\">Cookies</h1>          \t \t\t\t<p class='govuk-body'>Cookies are small files saved on your phone, tablet or computer when you visit a website.</p>         \t\t\t<p class='govuk-body'>We use an essential cookie to keep your data secure while you use the Warm Homes: Local Grant/Social Housing Decarbonisation Fund reporting service.</p>   \t\t\t<p class='govuk-body'>We do not need to ask permission to use essential cookies.</p>          \t \t\t<h2 class=\"govuk-heading-m\">Functional cookies</h2>          \t \t\t\t<p class='govuk-body'>These functional cookies help improve the user experience. This service can operate without these functional cookies, but doing so may reduce site functionality depending on the purpose of the blocked cookie. You can find out more about these cookies at <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://help.salesforce.com/s/articleView?id=sf.networks_cookies.htm&language=en_US&type=5&utm_source=chatgpt.com\">Salesforce Help.</a></p>           \t\t\t<table class=\"govuk-table\">              \t\t\t\t<caption class=\"govuk-visually-hidden\">Functional cookies/caption>              \t\t\t\t<thead class=\"govuk-table__head\">                  \t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">Name</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">Purpose</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">Expires</th>                 </tr>             </thead>              \t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody class=\"govuk-table__body\">                  \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">_ga</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Distinguishes users</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">2 years</td>                 </tr> <tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">_ga_container-id</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Persists session state</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">2 years</td>                 </tr> <tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">_gid</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Distinguishes users</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">24 Hours <tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">_gat</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Throttles request rate</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">1 minute</td>                 </tr>                                                    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">{UserId}_KMPage</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">In Salesforce, reads the last user selection for 'Find in View', 'Article Language', {DataCategory}, and 'Validation Status' in Article Management.</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">1 day</td>                 </tr>              \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">{UserId}_KnowledgePageDispatcher</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">In Salesforce, remembers the user selection to determine whether to show 'Articles' or 'My Drafts' view in Knowledge.</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Session</td>                 </tr> \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">{UserId}_KnowledgePageFilter{DataCategory}</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">In Salesforce, remembers the last user selection for the data category filter in Knowledge.</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Session</td>                 </tr> \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">{UserId}_KnowledgePageFilterArticleArticleType</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">In Salesforce, remembers the last user selection for the article type filter for 'Articles' view in Knowledge.</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Session</td>                 </tr> \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">{UserId}_KnowledgePageFilterArticlePublishStatus</th>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">In Salesforce, remembers the last user selection for the publish status filter for 'Articles' view in Knowledge.</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Session</td>                 </tr> \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr role=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__row\">                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" class=\"govuk-table__header\">{UserId}_KnowledgePageFilterArticleValidationStatus</th>                     \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">In Salesforce, remembers the last user selection for the validation status filter for 'Articles' view in Knowledge.</td>                      \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"govuk-table__cell\">Session</td>                 </tr> \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tbody> \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t         </table> \t\t\t\t\t\t  \t </div> </div>          </main>    